### you must need dso-supported proftpd ( ./configure --enabole-dso )  ###

### 1: compile && install

   $ /path/to/proftpd/bin/prxs -c mod_limit_login_post_pass.c -i

### 2: edit config

   $ emacs proftpd.conf
   LoadModule mod_limit_login_post_pass.c

### 3: restart proftpd

### 4: edit .ftpaccess

    <Limit LOGIN>
      DenyAll
    </Limit>

### 5: let's test

    $ ftp localhost 
